WHILE program is running

    Listen for user input
    
    IF has user input THEN
    
        Set INPUT to input value.
        Split INPUT into an array of words.
        Parse array of words.
    
        IF pre-programmed action THEN
        
            Attempt to run the action.
        
        ELSEIF searchable on Wolfram Alpha THEN
        
            Return the search result on Wolfram Alpha on screen
            Begin reading the results
        
        ELSE
        
            Say that JARVIS does not understand
        
        ENDIF
    
    ENDIF

ENDWHILE
